Language Model Tectonics (LMT)
Copyright 2026 Mossrake Group, LLC

This product includes Language Model Tectonics, a drift detection tool for
language model endpoints, developed by Mossrake Group, LLC
(https://mossrake.ai).

Language Model Tectonics detects and dates change in model endpoints.
It does not rank, grade, or judge them.

LMT emits drift evidence conformant to the Mossrake Language Model
Diligence specification (https://github.com/mossrake/lmd-spec).

